content: Hi channel. I am new to this chat. I tried the rustwasm discord server but it seems to be moved to here. I have a question regarding wasm-pack. Is this the corret place?
@Nick Fitzgerald might know what's up, the rustwasm team repo is no longer updated and he's the only remaining WG member. But I don't see any WASM stream here.
Or you could ask directly. Zulip is geared towards compiler contributors, but the general stream has all kinds of conversations. It probably won't be out of place.
Haven't heard of WASM moving to this server. Maybe they created a separate zulip instance for rust-wasm?
